<text top="72" left="208" width="199" height="12" font="0"><b>ORDER OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE </b></text>
<text top="84" left="179" width="258" height="12" font="0"><b>INTER-AMERICAN COURT OF HUMAN RIGHTS </b></text>
<text top="96" left="237" width="142" height="12" font="0"><b>OF SEPTEMBER 25, 1997 </b></text>
<text top="108" left="306" width="3" height="12" font="0"><b> </b></text>
<text top="120" left="233" width="152" height="12" font="0"><b>PROVISIONAL MEASURES  </b></text>
<text top="133" left="306" width="3" height="12" font="0"><b> </b></text>
<text top="145" left="245" width="55" height="12" font="0"><b>ÁLVAREZ </b></text>
<text top="145" left="300" width="35" height="12" font="1"><i><b>ET AL.</b></i></text>
<text top="145" left="335" width="36" height="12" font="0"><b> CASE </b></text>
<text top="157" left="306" width="3" height="12" font="0"><b> </b></text>
<text top="169" left="90" width="3" height="12" font="0"><b> </b></text>
<text top="181" left="90" width="3" height="12" font="0"><b> </b></text>
<text top="193" left="90" width="86" height="12" font="0"><b>HAVING SEEN: </b></text>
<text top="205" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="217" left="90" width="16" height="12" font="2">1. </text>
<text top="217" left="126" width="402" height="12" font="2">The order of the Inter-American Court of Human Rights of September 19, </text>
<text top="230" left="90" width="130" height="12" font="2">1997, in which it decided </text>
<text top="242" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="254" left="126" width="363" height="10" font="3">to convene the Inter-American Commission on Human Rights and the State of Colombia </text>
<text top="263" left="126" width="364" height="10" font="3">to a public hearing to be held at the seat of the Court on November 4, 1997, at 10.00 </text>
<text top="273" left="126" width="363" height="10" font="3">a.m., to hear their arguments on the provisional measures requested in the [.] [Álvarez </text>
<text top="283" left="126" width="21" height="10" font="4"><i>et al.</i></text>
<text top="283" left="147" width="30" height="10" font="3">] case. </text>
<text top="292" left="126" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="305" left="90" width="89" height="12" font="0"><b>CONSIDERING: </b></text>
<text top="317" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="329" left="126" width="400" height="12" font="2">That, having reviewed the agenda of work for the XXXVIII Regular Session of </text>
<text top="341" left="90" width="436" height="12" font="2">the Inter-American Court of Human Rights, the President considered it necessary to </text>
<text top="353" left="90" width="436" height="12" font="2">restructure this in order to accomplish the planned objectives and therefore the date </text>
<text top="365" left="90" width="437" height="12" font="2">of the public hearing established by this Court in its order of September 19, 1997, </text>
<text top="377" left="90" width="95" height="12" font="2">must be modified. </text>
<text top="389" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="401" left="90" width="74" height="12" font="0"><b>THEREFORE: </b></text>
<text top="414" left="90" width="3" height="12" font="0"><b> </b></text>
<text top="426" left="90" width="288" height="12" font="0"><b>THE PRESIDENT OF THE INTER-AMERICAN COURT  </b></text>
<text top="438" left="90" width="118" height="12" font="0"><b>OF HUMAN RIGHTS,  </b></text>
<text top="450" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="462" left="90" width="436" height="12" font="2">pursuant to Article 12.2 of the Statute of the Inter-American Court of Human Rights </text>
<text top="474" left="90" width="433" height="12" font="2">and Article 4 of the Rules of Procedure of the Inter-American Court of Human Rights, </text>
<text top="486" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="498" left="90" width="58" height="12" font="0"><b>DECIDES: </b></text>
<text top="511" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="523" left="126" width="401" height="12" font="2">To convene the Inter-American Commission on Human Rights and the State </text>
<text top="535" left="90" width="436" height="12" font="2">of Colombia to a public hearing to be held at the seat of the Inter-American Court of </text>
<text top="547" left="90" width="436" height="12" font="2">Human Rights on November 8, 1997, at 10.00 a.m., in order to hear their arguments </text>
<text top="559" left="90" width="436" height="12" font="2">on the provisional measures requested in the instant case, and a hearing prior to this </text>
<text top="571" left="90" width="158" height="12" font="2">at 9.00 a.m. on the same day. </text>
<text top="583" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="595" left="90" width="4" height="12" font="2"> </text>
<text top="608" left="393" width="133" height="12" font="2">Hernán Salgado-Pesantes </text>
<text top="620" left="409" width="86" height="12" font="2">          President </text>
